c: 5
v: 103
t: "Ma uusan amrin Allaah (yeelashada) Baxiirah (xoolo caanahooda sanamyada loo bixiyo) ama Saa’ ibah (xoolo sanamyada dartood loo sii daayo) ama Wasiilah (xoolo sanamyada lagu sadaqeysto) ama Xaam (riti sanamyada loo daayo) laakiinse gaaladu waxay ka been sheegaan Allaah, badankooduna ma laha garasho"